notesStmt.note: Imperfect at the beginning. Folios wanting after folio 263.
Folio 274r contains a short note, and folio 274v is concerned with a valid contract of marriage.
Zekharyah and Yosef ben Benayah ben Se'adyah ben Margah ben Shelomoh: inscribed, folio 273v, both notes crossed out.
Manuscript description based on Margoliouth, G.: Catalogue of the Hebrew and Samaritan Manuscripts in the British Museum, London 1965.
